	<div class="post_content">
		<h2>16 Social Media Tools The Experts Swear By</h2>			<div class="post_details clrfix">  
									<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/0bc44b949de12d8e441731acd0db6a43?s=36&amp;d=&amp;r=R' class='avatar avatar-36 photo' height='36' width='36' />					<span class="posted_by">by <a href="http://www.socialfresh.com/contributors/social-fresh/">Social Fresh</a> on Jun 25, 2014</span>
										<div class="user-social clrfix">
			<span class="follow_on_twitter">
			<a href="http://twitter.com/socialfresh" class="twitter-follow-button" data-show-count="false">Follow @socialfresh</a>
		</span>
	
	</div>
		<div class="share_buttons_wrapper clrfix">
